{B01: Scandinavian Defence} 1. e4 d5 2. exd5 Qxd5 3. Nc3 Qd6 4. Be2 Nf6 5. Nf3
Nc6 (5... a6 6. d3 Nc6 7. Ne4 Nxe4 8. dxe4 e5 9. c3 Qg6 10. O-O Be7 11. Qc2 Bh3
12. Ne1 Bc5 13. Kh1 Be6 14. f4 exf4 15. Bxf4 O-O-O 16. Nf3 Rhe8 17. b4 Ba7 18.
