{D56: Queen's Gambit Declined: Lasker Defence} 1. d4 d5 2. c4 e6 3. Nf3 Nf6 4.
Bg5 Be7 5. Nc3 h6 6. Bh4 O-O 7. e3 Nc6 (7... c6 8. Bd3 (8. cxd5 exd5 9. Bd3 Be6
10. h3 Nbd7 11. O-O Ne8 12. Bg3 Bd6 13. Ne5 Nxe5 14. dxe5 Bc7 15. e4 dxe4 16.
Nxe4 Qe7 17. Re1 Rd8 18. Qc2 Bf5 19. Nd6 Bxd3 20. Qxd3 Bb6 21. a4 Qe6 22. Qc3
Rd7 {Georgiev,V (2517)-Mamedjarova,Z (2349) Wijk aan Zee 2005 1-0 (35)}) 8...
dxc4 9. Bxc4 b5 10. Bd3 Bb7 11. O-O Nbd7 12. a3 a5 13. Qe2 b4 14. Na4 {1/2-1/2
(14) Moiseenko,A (2627)-Kharlov,A (2581) Istanbul 2003}) 8. Rc1 $146 (8. Bd3
Nb4 9. Be2 dxc4 10. Bxc4 c5 11. O-O cxd4 12. Qxd4 Qa5 13. Qe5 Nc6 14. Qxa5 Nxa5
15. Bd3 Nc6 16. Rfd1 Rd8 17. Bb5 Bd7 18. h3 Be8 19. Kf1 Rxd1+ 20. Rxd1 Rd8 21.
Rxd8 Bxd8 22. a3 Kf8 {Sanguineti,R (2530)-Naranja,R (2395) Nice 1974 1/2-1/2})
8... a6 {Secures b5} 9. a3 {Consolidates b4} dxc4 10. Bxc4 Nd5 11. Bg3 Nxc3 12.
Rxc3 Bd6 13. O-O Bxg3 14. hxg3 Qf6 (14... Ne7 15. g4 $14) 15. Qc2 Rd8 16. Rd1
Rd6 17. Ba2 Bd7 (17... Rd8 18. Rc5 $16) 18. Rc5 (18. Nd2 Qd8 19. Ne4 Rd5 $18)
18... Rd8 (18... Qe7 19. Nd2 $16) 19. Rh5 (19. e4 e5 20. Nxe5 Be6 21. Nxc6 Rxc6
22. Rxc6 bxc6 $16) 19... Qg6 (19... g5 $5 {deserves consideration} 20. Rf1 e5
21. Nxg5 hxg5 22. Qh7+ Kf8 $14) 20. Qxg6 $16 fxg6 21. Rc5 Kf8 22. Rdc1 Ke7 23.
Nd2 Be8 24. Ne4 R6d7 25. R5c3 Rb8 26. b4 Rdd8 27. Nc5 Bd7 (27... Rd6 28. f4 $16
) 28. Bb1 Be8 (28... Na7 $5 $16) 29. Be4 $18 Rd6 (29... a5 30. Bxc6 bxc6 31.
bxa5 Rb5 $18) 30. Bf3 $4 {there were better ways to keep up the pressure} (30.
Nxa6 Rc8 31. Nc5 Rb8 $18) 30... g5 $2 (30... Nd8 31. g4 $16) 31. Nb3 (31. Nxa6
$142 $5 bxa6 32. Bxc6 Bxc6 33. Rxc6 $18) 31... Bd7 32. Rc4 g6 33. a4 (33. Nc5
Nd8 $18) 33... Kf6 (33... h5 34. Nc5 $16) 34. Nc5 $18 Ke7 35. b5 (35. Nxd7 $5
Rxd7 36. Bxc6 bxc6 37. Rxc6 Rxb4 38. Rxa6 Rb6 $18) 35... axb5 $16 36. axb5 Na5
(36... Na7 $142 $5 37. R4c2 Nxb5 38. Nxb7 Rb6 $16) 37. Nxd7 $18 Rxd7 38. Rxc7
b6 39. Rc8 Rd8 (39... Rxc8 40. Rxc8 h5 41. Rb8 $18) 40. R1c7+ Kf6 41. Rxb8 Rxb8
42. Kf1 (42. g4 Rf8 $18) 42... h5 43. g4 h4 (43... Rh8 44. Ke2 $18) 44. Ke2 Nb3
(44... Rd8 $142 $18) 45. Kd3 Na5 46. e4 (46. Bc6 $142 $5 {keeps an even firmer
grip} Rf8 $18) 46... e5 47. d5 Rd8 (47... Rb7 48. Rc8 $16) 48. Bd1 $18 Rd6 49.
Rh7 (49. Ba4 Rd8 $18) 49... Rd8 50. f4 (50. Ra7 $5 Rc8 $18) 50... gxf4 $16 51.
Rxh4 (51. g5+ $142 Kxg5 52. Re7 $16) 51... Kg5 $4 {letting the wind out of his
own sails} (51... Nb7 $142 {the rescuing straw} 52. Bf3 Nc5+ 53. Kc3 Ra8 $11)
52. Rh7 $18 Rd6 (52... Re8 53. Rf7 $18) 53. Re7 (53. Rf7 $5 {makes it even
easier for White} Kh4 54. Re7 Kg3 55. Rxe5 Kxg2 $18) 53... Kf6 54. Re8 Nb7 55.
g5+ $1 {Deflection: e5} Kf7 (55... Kxg5 56. Rxe5+ {Deflection}) 56. Rxe5 Nc5+
57. Kd4 Nd7 $4 {Black falls apart} (57... Rd7 $18) 58. Re6 $1 {a beautiful,
forced end to the game} Rxe6 59. dxe6+ Kxe6 (59... Ke8 {is not the saving move}
60. exd7+ Kxd7 61. Bg4+ Kd8 62. Kd5 f3 63. gxf3 Ke7 64. e5 Kf8 65. Kd6 Ke8 66.
e6 Kf8 67. Kd7 Kg7 68. e7 Kg8 69. e8=Q+ Kg7 70. Be6 Kh7 71. Qg8#) 60. Bg4+ Kd6
(60... Kf7 {a fruitless try to alter the course of the game} 61. Bxd7 f3 62.
gxf3 Ke7 63. Bh3 Ke8 64. e5 Ke7 65. Kd5 Ke8 66. Kd6 Kf8 67. e6 Kg8 68. e7 Kf7
69. Kd7 Kg8 70. e8=Q+ Kh7 71. Be6 Kg7 72. Qg8#) 61. Bxd7 Kxd7 62. Ke5 Ke7 63.
Kxf4 Ke6 64. Ke3 Ke5 (64... Kf7 {does not improve anything} 65. e5 Ke7 66. Kd4
Ke6 67. Ke4 Kf7 68. Kd5 Ke7 69. e6 Ke8 70. Kd6 Kf8 71. g4 Kg7 72. e7 Kg8 73.
e8=Q+ Kh7 74. Qe7+ Kg8 75. Ke6 Kh8 76. Kf6 Kg8 77. Qg7#) 65. g3 Ke6 66. Kd4 Kd6
67. e5+ Ke6 68. Ke4 Ke7 69. Kd5 Kd7 70. e6+ Ke7 (70... Kc7 {doesn't get the
bull off the ice} 71. Ke5 Kc8 72. Kd6 Kd8 73. e7+ Ke8 74. g4 Kf7 75. Kd7 Kg8
76. e8=Q+ Kg7 77. Ke7 Kh7 78. Kf8 Kh8 79. Kf7+ Kh7 80. Qg8#) 71. Ke5 Ke8 72.
