{A80: Dutch Defence: Unusual White second moves} 1. d4 f5 2. Nf3 Nf6 3. e3 d6
$146 {Covers e5} (3... e6 4. Be2 g6 (4... b6 5. b3 (5. O-O Bb7 6. c4 Bd6 7. Nc3
O-O 8. d5 Na6 9. Nd4 Nc5 10. Bf3 Nfe4 11. Bxe4 Nxe4 12. Nxe4 fxe4 13. dxe6 Qh4
14. g3 Qh3 15. exd7 c5 16. Nf5 Rf6 17. Nh4 g5 18. Qh5 gxh4 19. Qg5+ Kf7 {
Fries Nielsen,J (2310)-Kristiansen,J (2365) Aalborg 1979 0-1 (41)}) 5... Bb7 6.
