14. Bxc4 d5 15. Bd3 Bd7 16. a4 Rfc8 17. Ne5 Be8 18. Qd2 {Nimzowitsch,
A-Tartakower,S Gothenburg 1920 1/2-1/2 (41)}) (3... g6 4. b3 Bg7 5. Bb2 O-O 6.
