13. Qxe4 Nf6 14. Qc2 Nh5 15. g3 Bf5 16. Bd3 Bxd3 17. Qxd3 g5 18. Rae1 {Hesse,P
(2330)-Heidrich,M (2385) Germany 1997 1/2-1/2}) 4. Bc4 e6 {Controls d5} 5. O-O
g6 6. Bb3 Bg7 7. Ng5 {White threatens to win material: Ng5xe6} Qe7 8. f4 O-O 9.
c4 h6 {Black threatens to win material: h6xg5} 10. Nf3 Kh7 11. Nc3 Nc6 12. d5 {
White threatens to win material: d5xc6} (12. a3 e5 $11) 12... Na5 $15 13. dxe6
(13. Bd2 $5 $15) 13... Bxe6 $17 14. Nd5 Bxd5 15. cxd5 Nxb3 16. Qxb3 c6 17. dxc6
bxc6 {Black has new hanging pawns: c6+d6} 18. Nd4 (18. Qc3 c5 $15) 18... Rfc8
19. Qc2 Qe8 20. Bd2 Ne4 21. Rae1 Nxd2 (21... Qg8 22. Nb3 $15) 22. Qxd2 $11 Rab8
23. b3 Qe4 24. Ne2 d5 25. Rf3 c5 26. Nc3 $2 (26. Rd1 Qe7 $15) 26... Bxc3 (26...
Qb4 $142 {Black missed this excellent chance} 27. Nb1 c4 28. Qxb4 Rxb4 29. bxc4
dxc4 $17) 27. Qxc3 $11 d4 (27... c4 $142 $5 $11 {is a viable option}) 28. exd4
$16 cxd4 29. Rxe4 (29. Qd2 $142 $5 Qd5 30. Rd3 $16) 29... dxc3 $11 {A double
rook endgame occured.} 30. Re7+ {White forks: a7} Kg8 31. Rf1 (31. Re1 c2 32.
Rc1 Rb6 $11) 31... c2 (31... Rb4 32. Re2 $15) 32. Rc1 $11 Rb4 (32... Rb5 $11)
33. g3 (33. Re2 Rxf4 34. Rexc2 Rxc2 35. Rxc2 Re4 $14) 33... Rd4 (33... Re4 $142
34. Rd7 Re2 $17) 34. Ree1 $4 {White has let it slip away} (34. Kf2 $142 {
would hold out} Rd1 35. Re1 $11) 34... Rd2 $19 35. h3 (35. b4 Kf7 36. Ra1 Re8
$19) 35... Rcd8 (35... Rc3 36. Re8+ Kf7 37. Ree1 Rxg3+ 38. Kf1 Rxh3 39. Kg1
Rg3+ 40. Kh1 $19) 36. Kf1 (36. g4 {is no salvation} R8d3 37. gxf5 Rg3+ 38. Kf1
